  "message": "fix(ci): remove rustfmt component to prevent toolchain conflict\n\nThe dtolnay/rust-toolchain action pre-installs rustfmt, causing a conflict\nwhen rust-toolchain.toml also requests it. Remove the component to allow\nthe workflow to use the pre-installed version.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
